{"tid":180740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【反恐演習】機場特警持MP5 離境大堂 射殺「恐怖份子」","createTime":"2017-03-31T06:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T21:10:50.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"190b925f51254594fa65e982e52986b0f5b45297","tid":180740,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490934028_d865.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490934028_d865.jpg&h=f113e7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490903748_f93b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490903748_f93b.jpg&h=9e696d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490902556_b8f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490902556_b8f2.jpg&h=cd964f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490902527_a2f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490902527_a2f1.jpg&h=7582cd7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【13：28更新】新增動新聞<br />\n赤鱲角機場以色列航空公司凌晨受到恐怖襲擊，機場特警保護要人，受到恐怖份子槍擊及炸彈施襲，機場特警成功保護要人，並將恐怖份子制服。以上情節僅是反恐演習，現實中沒有出現。<br />\n<br />\n今次演習是機場特警與以色列航空公司及機管局聯合進行，模擬乘客混亂情況，以致遇到恐怖襲擊如何處理。機場特警及以色列航空公司，分別出動40人及20人，機管局有數人觀察。演習由凌晨1時至凌晨4時。由最初簡單的乘客鼓噪開始，提升至打架產生混亂及藏有武器，直至有槍擊及發現炸彈，約有4至5個演習case。由於避免影響到乘客，槍擊不會發出聲響。<br />\n據稱，機場特警不時進行演習，其中大型演習每年1至2次，由於以色列航空公司保安經驗較為豐富，所以合作較多。"},{"pid":"71ff03d39877c8ac609bc37dc0d5af5eb2ef584c","tid":180740,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"上次行山果對狗男女有冇份參加"},{"pid":"cd55a12e6c6f35ae7ca8a773e46ad3c7fab86b1f","tid":180740,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"行山果條撚樣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7b6458b51a4a88d835ffef159b359abf1db150","tid":180740,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:31:04.000Z","msg":"會唔會係機場迷路架"},{"pid":"8c01a3a0346c747a492d465227077440d2296b5b","tid":180740,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:32:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"402ef44dbfa807cc94636ab8703e9cf0bfbc57ad","tid":180740,"uid":5858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170331/large/1490903748_f93b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170331%2Flarge%2F1490903748_f93b.jpg&h=9e696d94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人諗起保持通話ending嗰幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca798e7fd06ec0cd0552eac73d6d3f36b225866","tid":180740,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T06:49:44.000Z","msg":"行山條撚樣呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241cb2233af79c9b64fbfd758ff9bf0d7ac2a7cd","tid":180740,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"行山條撚樣呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f856e788d92f0e417e523421e4bf5d91140484c7","tid":180740,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:49:06.000Z","msg":"多數因為出左行山單野, 所以要搞呢D公關SHOW"},{"pid":"c478daa2233050f16a9a51e4ea7c2c8d37061fe1","tid":180740,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"其實我一直都唔明依啲演習既實